title: EP22 The Fabulous Bill Barrett
itunes:title: The Fabulous Bill Barrett
description: Bill Barrett has been the voice of Dan Carlin’s podcasts since they began in 2005. In this retrospective Dan looks back at samples of Bill’s catalog of  work.
